Use the following commands to clone/install everything need for a new wordpress website using AFBFramework.

##STEPS FOR NEW SITE SETUP##
---

1. git clone https://github.com/stevecordle/AFGDefault.git .
1. git submodule init
1. git submodule update
1. composer selfupdate
1. composer update
1. cd wordpress && git checkout 4.1.1 (or current Version)

---
Copy paste the below to go thru all of the steps with one line



    git clone https://github.com/stevecordle/AFGDefault.git . && git submodule init && git submodule update && composer selfupdate && composer update && cd wordpress && git checkout 4.1.1 && cd ..
